title: 11/24/20 HOUR 2- Tom Izzo and Josh Duhamel
itunes:title: 11/24/20 HOUR 2- Tom Izzo and Josh Duhamel
description:
Tom Izzo talks to Dan about his battle with Covid19. Tom says that Covid19 is no joke and that he quarantined for 11 days. Josh Duhamel tells Dan about his upcoming movie and his Vikings fandom.
